quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  38,1,"Sad walqur-ani theeaththikr"
  38,2,"Bali allatheena kafaroo fee AAizzatinwashiqaq"
  38,3,"Kam ahlakna min qablihim min qarninfanadaw walata heena manas"
  38,4,"WaAAajiboo an jaahum munthirunminhum waqala alkafiroona hatha sahirunkaththab"
  38,5,"AjaAAala al-alihata ilahan wahidaninna hatha lashay-on AAujab"
  38,6,"Wantalaqa almalao minhum aniimshoo wasbiroo AAala alihatikuminna hatha lashay-on yurad"
  38,7,"Ma samiAAna bihatha feealmillati al-akhirati in hatha illa ikhtilaq"
  38,8,"Aonzila AAalayhi aththikru minbaynina bal hum fee shakkin min thikree bal lammayathooqoo AAathab"
  38,9,"Am AAindahum khaza-inu rahmatirabbika alAAazeezi alwahhab"
  38,10,"Am lahum mulku assamawatiwal-ardi wama baynahuma falyartaqoofee al-asbab"
  38,11,"Jundun ma hunalika mahzoomunmina al-ahzab"
  38,12,"Kaththabat qablahum qawmu noohinwaAAadun wafirAAawnu thoo al-awtad"
  38,13,"Wathamoodu waqawmu lootin waas-habual-aykati ola-ika al-ahzab"
  38,14,"In kullun illa kaththaba arrusulafahaqqa AAiqab"
  38,15,"Wama yanthuru haola-iilla sayhatan wahidatan ma lahamin fawaq"
  38,16,"Waqaloo rabbana AAajjil lanaqittana qabla yawmi alhisab"
